template.name: Template App Mysql Service
template.description:
UserParameter=mysql.status,mysql --defaults-file=/etc/zabbix/.my.cnf --defaults-group-suffix=_monitoring -N -e "SHOW GLOBAL STATUS" | awk '{print """ $1 "":"" $2 """}' | sed ':a;N;$!ba;s/
/,/g' | sed 's/^/{/' | sed 's/$/}/' UserParameter=mysql.config,mysql --defaults-file=/etc/zabbix/.my.cnf --defaults-group-suffix=_monitoring -N -e "SHOW GLOBAL VARIABLES" | awk '{print """ $1 "":"" $2 """}' | sed ':a;N;$!ba;s/
/,/g' | sed 's/^/{/' | sed 's/$/}/' UserParameter=mysql.slave,mysql --defaults-file=/etc/zabbix/.my.cnf --defaults-group-suffix=_monitoring -e "SHOW SLAVE STATUS\G" | awk '{gsub(":",""); if(NR>1)print """ $1 "":"" $2 """}' | sed ':a;N;$!ba;s/
/,/g' | sed 's/^/{/' | sed 's/$/}/'
# Requires Process privileges UserParameter=mysql.innodb_active_transactions,mysql --defaults-file=/etc/zabbix/.my.cnf --defaults-group-suffix=_monitoring -N -e "SELECT count(*) as count FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.INNODB_TRX"
UserParameter=mysql.ping,mysqladmin --defaults-file=/etc/zabbix/.my.cnf ping | grep -c alive UserParameter=mysql.version,mysql -V

trigger.name: MySQL active threads more than 40 on {HOST.NAME}
MySQL active threads more than 100 on {HOST.NAME}
MySQL connections utilization more than 80% on {HOST.NAME}

dependency.name: MySQL connections utilization more than 95% on {HOST.NAME}

trigger.name: MySQL connections utilization more than 95% on {HOST.NAME}
